"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n起個公園仔既話 好奇怪 <br />\n附近係高樓大廈 完全冇緩沖空間 一入到去壓逼感仲大<br />\n<br />\n不過果邊已經咁塞車塞人 仲起咁多寫字樓頂唔頂得順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b27d5f599169981e16771cddd2ff5763d74561","tid":493802,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T04:36:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16cdd201d558463fb1a5f7cd126f92f5be05f62d","tid":493802,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T05:18:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拆撚左佢啦<br />\n<br />\n又舊又臭<br />\n<br />\n起個公園仔比人坐下都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係俾賓賓坐咋~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6491ce027ea36abe9ce3fa5b80f76cb67dfc857b","tid":493802,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T05:21:14.000Z","msg":"環團叫人拆野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440dcb4a96ff6ac0371df92f497feb6e2132a277","tid":493802,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T05:23:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持   又唔拆又唔重建想點</blockquote><br />\n十幾廿年睇住佢廢左係度 唔知想點"},{"pid":"4eba5c3bd6d3e39a54c085306649a7c6056eb3e8","tid":493802,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T05:24:14.000Z","msg":"何來拖足十年又搵第二個黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}